信息化要求但无法实现，企业无法养 IT 团队，需要外包的</p>\n<p>目标行业：房产中介公司、教育培训机构(中小型)、三方销售公司(没有产品，专门代理卖货)</p>\n<p>核心功能：简易 OA + 在线签约 + 绩效管理 + 运营看板 + 合同管理(中介) + 课程安排(培训) + 客户关系(微信公众号小程序)</p>\n<p>目标运营：6 个月(开发) + 3 个月(市场)</p>\n<p>PS：以上核心功能有做过，以前是定制给某客户做，现在想要产品化</p>\n<p>大家觉得有搞头吗，欢迎拍砖建议</p>\n", "last_modified": 1714511844, "replies": 49, "id": 1037137}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_large.png?m=1650127314", "name": "beijing", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_normal.png?m=1650127314", "title": "北京", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/beijing", "topics": 4024, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Beijing", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_mini.png?m=1650127314", "stars": 2241, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 19, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 7657, "username": "pursuit", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/pursuit", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8267/4fc2/7657_mini.png?m=1713182579", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8267/4fc2/7657_normal.png?m=1713182579", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8267/4fc2/7657_large.png?m=1713182579", "created": 1302064823, "last_modified": 1713182579}, "last_reply_by": "leeolsen", "last_touched": 1714543827, "title": "有跟我一样没赶上高铁的嘛", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1037215", "created": 1714526160, "deleted": 0, "content": "出门墨迹也好，对象拖延也好，路上堵车也好，没选地铁也好….. 总之没赶上高铁。恰逢假期，也没当天其他票了……", "content_rendered": "出门墨迹也好，对象拖延也好，路上堵车也好，没选地铁也好….. 总之没赶上高铁。恰逢假期，也没当天其他票了……", "last_modified": 1714526160, "replies": 44, "id": 1037215}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1695370146", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1695370146", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 16943, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些